{"lastModified":1768906039552,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::7f06beb0-c9fe-11f0-b4c1-09d317373933","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nIntroducing the Hanse 388 to the MK Yacht Explorer Fleet!\n\nWe’re delighted to announce the arrival of the Hanse 388 to the growing MK Yacht Explorer Fleet, now available from Marina Baotić, Croatia. Known for its sleek lines, modern design, and outstanding sailing performance, this yacht is perfect for both leisurely charters and skill-building adventures.\n\nWith 3 spacious cabins and 2 heads, the Hanse 388 offers comfort for up to 6-8 guests. Its bright, thoughtfully designed interior ensures a welcoming atmosphere, while its performance-oriented deck layout and easy handling make it a top choice for enthusiasts.\n\nThe Hanse 388 is also ideal for training sessions with a professional skipper, whether you’re just starting your sailing journey or looking to enhance your skills. As part of the MK Yacht Explorer Fleet, this yacht ensures high standards of quality and reliability, catering to both recreational sailors and those seeking a more immersive experience.\n\nWhy book this yacht?\n\nPart of the renowned MK Yacht Explorer Fleet, known for excellence.\nA versatile option for family charters, friend groups, or training programs.\nConveniently located at Marina Baotić, a premium hub for Adriatic sailing.\nPerfect for exploring Croatia’s stunning coastline and islands.\nSet sail aboard the Hanse 388 and experience the adventure and expertise of the MK Yacht Explorer Fleet!","blueprint":{"name":"FUFU","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::7f06beb0-c9fe-11f0-b4c1-09d317373933::assets::7eff6020-ca08-11f0-bd15-51168428bee3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7f06beb0-c9fe-11f0-b4c1-09d317373933::assets::7efe0090-ca08-11f0-bd15-51168428bee3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7f06beb0-c9fe-11f0-b4c1-09d317373933::assets::7efe27a0-ca08-11f0-bd15-51168428bee3/{imageVariant}","/